text: Poboishche () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Poboishchensky Selsoviet, Kugarchinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 194 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 55 km from Mrakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kugarchinsky District
title: Poboishche
